list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Added code to auto initialize commands without needing a quick start, shoutouts to Victorique on discord.
Added code to auto clean up guilds after the bot leaves a discord on Mongo.
Created clientSettings file for actual reusability

task.summary:
A complete rework of AniDay in typescript
Helpers: -buttons: organizes all of the inter-actable button elements into a seperate file -daily: responsible for formatting embeds, picking out random anime from a day for the auto poster, and returns every anime for the daily command -mongo: everything mongo is here, functions for fetching days, updating them, etc. are all here
Commands: -slashCommands: All of the slash commands live here, they pull a lot of functions from the helpers and in a way kinda acts like an android app. The helpers can be seen like fragments and slashCommands is the activity they live on.
Models: -Contains the mongodb model and the shortFull model for when a daily command is expanded or shortened
